thread.title: U.K. Authorities Raid Cambridge Analytica Office in London

author: wsjcom
title: U.K. Authorities Raid Cambridge Analytica Office in London

organizations.name: u.k. authorities raid cambridge analytica office

text:
LONDON—Officers from Britain’s information regulator raided the offices of data firm Cambridge Analytica after being granted a warrant as part of an investigation into alleged misuse of personal information.
A High Court judge granted the warrant Friday evening. Soon afterward, 18 people, some in Information Commissioner’s Office jackets, entered the company’s central London offices.
